articles.title: Trudeau to bring up Trump’s threat to annex Canada in meeting with King Charles - The Tribune India
articles.description: The king has come under criticism in Canada for being silent about Trump's threats to annex Canada.
articles.content:
Canadian Prime Minister Justin Trudeau will meet King Charles III, the country's head of state, on Monday where he will discuss US President Donald Trump's threats to make Canada the 51st state.
